---
// VIN Values: Rediseño minimalista blanco y negro impactante
---

<section class="relative bg-white py-20 sm:py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      
      <div class="text-center mb-20 sm:mb-32">
        <div class="relative inline-block">
          <h2 class="text-6xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-black text-zinc-900 leading-none tracking-tighter">
            V.I.N.
          </h2>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 text-6xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-black text-zinc-100 leading-none tracking-tighter translate-x-2 translate-y-2 -z-10">
            V.I.N.
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl text-zinc-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Nuestros principios fundamentales
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-0">
        
        <div class="group relative border border-zinc-900 p-12 sm:p-16 hover:bg-zinc-900 transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-[12rem] sm:text-[16rem] font-black text-zinc-100 leading-none select-none group-hover:text-zinc-800 transition-colors pointer-events-none">
            V
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="mb-8">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-zinc-400 group-hover:text-zinc-500 transition-colors">
                01
              </span>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-zinc-900 mb-6 tracking-tight group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
              Visión
            </h3>
            
            <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors">
              Vemos más allá del código. Entendemos tu negocio y traducimos tu visión en soluciones digitales que transforman.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-8 w-16 h-px bg-zinc-900 group-hover:bg-white transition-colors"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative border border-zinc-900 p-12 sm:p-16 bg-zinc-900 hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300">
          <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-[12rem] sm:text-[16rem] font-black text-zinc-800 leading-none select-none group-hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors pointer-events-none">
            I
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="mb-8">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-zinc-500 group-hover:text-zinc-400 transition-colors">
                02
              </span>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-tight group-hover:text-zinc-900 transition-colors">
              Integridad
            </h3>
            
            <p class="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-zinc-600 transition-colors">
              Sin vueltas. Sin promesas vacías. Comunicación clara, plazos reales y transparencia total en cada etapa del proyecto.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-8 w-16 h-px bg-white group-hover:bg-zinc-900 transition-colors"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative border border-zinc-900 p-12 sm:p-16 hover:bg-zinc-900 transition-all duration-300 md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-[12rem] sm:text-[16rem] font-black text-zinc-100 leading-none select-none group-hover:text-zinc-800 transition-colors pointer-events-none">
            N
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="mb-8">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-zinc-400 group-hover:text-zinc-500 transition-colors">
                03
              </span>
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black text-zinc-900 mb-6 tracking-tight group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
              Notoriedad
            </h3>
            
            <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed group-hover:text-zinc-300 transition-colors">
              Tu presencia digital no pasa desapercibida. Creamos experiencias memorables que destacan y dejan huella.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-8 w-16 h-px bg-zinc-900 group-hover:bg-white transition-colors"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-20 sm:mt-32 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-12 sm:w-16 h-px bg-zinc-900"></div>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-zinc-900">
            Esto es VIN Studio
          </p>
          <div class="w-12 sm:w-16 h-px bg-zinc-900"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
